2nAy-ZbzLhAgFQtu9FgdSiUZFSqTvbqWrt6kp0YOqkEqWQXayr8Q38ApAONYQ], and in a re=
cent Not Boring Founders convo with Stilt=E2=80=99s Rohit Mittal [https://e=
mail.mg2.substack.com/c/eJxFkLtuwzAMRb_GGg1Zj8geNARt06FApg5BF0MP2lFjS4Ikt_D=
