Twk3k]. Fintech Today=E2=80=99s Ian Kar [https://email.mg2.substack.com/c/e=
JxFkMGOhCAMhp9mOBpEGPXAYS_7GqTS6rCjYKDuxLdfZjxs0rRpmvbv93tgWlI-7Z4Ki3dyfO5k=
I73KSsyUxVEou4C2vauhM3oUaDW2gxlEKG7ORBuE1XI-SOzHtAYPHFL8bEipjHjYUWov9XjvCcw=
